    nahi mila. Azad result sweekar karke responsible opposition aur public service
    ka sankalp leta hai.
  chapterNumber: 19
  nextChapterScene: 
  introTitle: CHAPTER 19 / PEHLA RASHTRIYA FAISLA
  introMessage: National stage par seva ka record zaroori hai, lekin pehli baar mein
    mandate milna guaranteed nahi.
  objectives:
  - {fileID: 1622707404}
  - {fileID: 1877574998}
  - {fileID: 1744646440}
